{"tid":329962,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"（等錢洗）有咩行業係可以好快咁搵到舊錢？","createTime":"2017-07-20T19:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T01:44:01.000Z","uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b73e81bcd0a983df73607f21b5046ee840f05cc3","tid":329962,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:05:00.000Z","msg":"認真問，有咩行業係可以好快咁搵到舊錢？"},{"pid":"4baf89e00768947e1f8fbfc0ecc9f0edd1cc1911","tid":329962,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:06:11.000Z","msg":"小弟不才，搵錢唔多，屋企人有事，突然好等錢用，想搵多份工去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e921e98e298c9676e6c71f8139b53dd6e48989","tid":329962,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:06:44.000Z","msg":"地盤"},{"pid":"0689f80880bcda50a0d314cd6a3038c066358fdb","tid":329962,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:09:58.000Z","msg":"要幾多先"},{"pid":"e84a6705f3cabfb01e261d1b0f67b60c3003445a","tid":329962,"uid":39608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:16:14.000Z","msg":"你返緊咩?工作時間?"},{"pid":"3755d6c372a1d7dae551c942a33f6c63233ad347","tid":329962,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:50:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要幾多先</blockquote><br />\n30000-50000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf31c0fc7b87d0a688122ba8857a2259d5b341a2","tid":329962,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:52:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你返緊咩?工作時間?</blockquote><br />\n岩岩轉行，辭左銀行份工，而家岩岩係保誠到做（唔好話我保險狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）岩岩入行未穩定，咁岩屋企又趕用錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f4b056d81a325526cdd06a80066c803ada14cf","tid":329962,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T20:16:00.000Z","msg":"借啦 幾萬蚊"},{"pid":"b6d96c40de06de897bbafecd098baf8301f80f9f","tid":329962,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T20:48:51.000Z","msg":"做雞"},{"pid":"1c027bda7f4471336457fea426c4b412803d701c","tid":329962,"uid":43979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T20:57:58.000Z","msg":"帶貨囉"},{"pid":"8f2d5c8c16e623110ce0adfc020c0c7b796cc74e","tid":329962,"uid":106340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T01:28:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1548fe855f14f917bef78a2b46970d9dee9b3998","tid":329962,"uid":27049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T01:31:56.000Z","msg":"保險<br />\n開曬所有家人朋友單之後就走"},{"pid":"f664f09b273b5ff4f01948c37d80024172a94789","tid":329962,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T01:36:03.000Z","msg":"男既做雞 女既做鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a11597c64d2dcd167ef33df95f7929f4b03f1a","tid":329962,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T01:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你返緊咩?工作時間?</blockquote><br />\n岩岩轉行，辭左銀行份工，而家岩岩係保誠到做（唔好話我保險狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）岩岩入行未穩定，咁岩屋企又趕用錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n銀行sale屎唔得咩？</blockquote><br />\n調左行好大壓力，間分行無人既，條數又大，個老闆又淨係識睇住條數，內部千瘡百孔<br />\n同埋做銀行sales好似好好咁，但其實仲無品過出面做保險既人多多聲，買完唔會幫手claim，無利益唔會幫人做野。所以先辭職"}]}